{"type": "article", "id": 39827, "title": "有关果酱的包装设计，总离不开甜美与自然｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2017-04-14T23:09:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 25708, "name": "果酱"}, {"id": 39530, "name": "Latona Marketing"}, {"id": 39531, "name": "Poco a Poco"}, {"id": 39532, "name": "meia.dúzia"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 356, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170414204241X9KdL18tcs4EO0Ig.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p class=\"\">随着人们越来越注重糖分的摄入情况，果酱的包装也变得收敛起来。得益于大自然的色谱，选用透明瓶身和镂空标签这类强调原材料本身的策略产生了不少简洁有力、视觉效果相当舒适的案例。本周的推荐就是这些甜而不腻的设计。</p><h3>meia.dúzia by Mariana Leal Rato</h3><p>既然大家多少都有过用果酱在面包上涂鸦的经历，为什么不把它们直接装进软管里呢？葡萄牙设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/marianalealrato\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mariana Leal Rato</a> 为当地果酱品牌 <a href=\"http://www.meiaduzia.pt/\" rel=\"nofollow\">meia.dúzia</a> 设计的包装就借鉴了人们熟悉的颜料管，不仅有趣还提升了果酱的便携性。标签的排版也格外干净利落，野餐时掏出一管真的可以起到以假乱真的效果。你可以通过<a href=\"http://store.meiaduzia.pt/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些甜蜜的“颜料”，售价从 5 欧元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204406ZXQELyHj0NGt68IU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664167\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204405h6szkUaeXPSGgOlq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204405flYqFTKZc5NBhHW9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204406hJ2LSryimCv7u6TE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.505833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Les Délices de Michèle by Chez Valois</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/9979453/Dlices-de-Michele-Brand-Identity-Packagings\" rel=\"nofollow\">Les Délices de Michèle</a> 来自加拿大，主推由魁北克本地的各种浆果制作而成的果酱。负责包装设计的 Chez Valois 工作室从原材料入手，将每一种原材料的照片同淡雅的水彩背景以及富有想象力的插画组合在一起，塑造出了一个温馨亲切的品牌形象，</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017041420442451KSvpqJzIHgVdEj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204426Rb4XmZrtThSY7Aok.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204427zdxa2HoXDq954Sum.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204426B5PVCrTzk4gbGeW9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Geleta by Dori Novotny</h3><p>什么样的果酱罐会让人在食用完后愿意把它们当装饰品放在桌上？匈牙利设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/dorinovo\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dori Novotny</a> 为 <a href=\"http://geletacukraszda.hu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Geleta</a> 餐厅出品的果酱所打造的包装或许会给你提供一些启发：它一共分为三种规格，其中小号和中号的罐头可以像积木那样垒起来以此组合成不同的礼盒装。礼盒的侧面还留有一条长方形的镂空，刚好可以显示同样采用镂空设计的果酱标签，给人一种一目了然的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204452nhcv8jwzDo231akt.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204450PjRbOkytfVvlrZhq.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.661667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204451Oz8QvjAUrD4PR2iY.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204451Ewo7dvKMH8hCDr1u.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204451uecWv51a6CQxVy4t.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ajá by Federico Parra &amp; Tatiana </h3><p>在哥伦比亚临近加勒比海的地区，一位被爱称为 Mama 的老奶奶会在每年圣诞节分发亲手制作的果酱和糖果。随着人气逐渐积累，越来越多的人开始向她提交订单，果酱生意也因此正式促成。为了强调品牌特有的人情味，负责设计的 Federico Parra 和 Tatiana Gómez 决定挑选与老奶奶有着紧密联系的要素，比如品牌名 <a href=\"http://www.packageinspiration.com/aja.html/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ajá</a> 就是老奶奶回应别人时的口癖，她在闲暇时的另一个手工爱好十字绣也成为了标签、订货单和名片上重要的视觉元素。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204559bOhXVfZaWny7dqBl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204559fAwO3FcLspdI4v0n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204559b7eI3HDlpzfTUPmo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204600vXgrOZMdLekwFSR4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204600Hy0sZpEatn54dPRU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>La Tía Fina by Juanma Aznar</h3><p>来自西班牙的 La Tía Fina 是一间生产果酱的家庭工坊，这种小批量的生产模式意味着操刀包装设计的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/juanma_azn4851\" rel=\"nofollow\">Juanma Aznar</a> 可以尝试更具手工感的设计元素。Aznar 最后采用拓印的方式为每款果酱打造了独一无二的图案，简单又富有诚意。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204631jxQhorIT8enV7s1K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204630lq71wX842Z9HtsPn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.727500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204629X3MsQpzDAFHIRuC5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.558333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204630tKFGn6EUQb408eJk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.704167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Poco a Poco by Latona Marketing</h3><p>还记得那些打着可食用噱头的指甲油吗？日本设计事务所 <a href=\"http://www.latona-m.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Latona Marketing</a> 为静冈县的手工果酱品牌 <a href=\"http://sweets-pocoapoco.shop/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Poco a Poco</a> 打造的包装走的是角色逆转的路线：设计师用四四方方的玻璃容器取代了传统的圆罐，并且在顶部添置了一个黑色的盖子。有了指甲油这一先入为主的印象，即便它其实是由轻质的硬纸制成的，也会让人产生一种需要费劲拧开的错觉。如果你对这些果酱感兴趣的话，可以通过 <a href=\"http://sweets-pocoapoco.shop/?mode=cate&amp;cbid=2242375&amp;csid=0\" rel=\"nofollow\">Poco a Poco</a> 的官方网站购买，售价从 800 日元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204704f8KZzPoqmCwiey9x.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204704bdVOnvgk6PtoSwIx.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204704d9jTNnDaHmgS7QPy.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170414204706AKQrZiTfjbu8gEO1.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}